dialog.add(artemis_thinking, "Turrets. Interesting. They have automated their defenses, which means they anticipated company eventually.");
dialog.add(artemis_talking, "Here is what my research tells me: the deeper layers were designed to be impossible for Mud People to navigate. No oxygen masks, no heat resistance, no way of surviving the pressure. And yet, here you are.");

